      <title>中国与菲律宾船只在南海再次发生碰撞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/chinese-philippine-vessels-collide-again-in-south-china-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，一艘中国海警船与一艘菲律宾船只在南海争议海域发生碰撞，这是加剧两国紧张局势的一系列事件中的最新一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/chinese-philippine-vessels-collide-again-in-south-china-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 09:20:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国坚决反对美国对俄罗斯相关实体实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/china-firmly-opposed-to-us-sanctions-on-russia-linked-entities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国企业被列入旨在针对俄罗斯供应链并阻碍其战时经济的制裁名单后，北京敦促美国“停止错误做法”。]]></description>
